1. On *stavlja* novac u banku. (He puts money in the bank.)
2. Ona *stavlja* šminku svaki dan. (She puts on makeup every day.)
3. Kada *stavite* hranu u frižider, ona se duže održava. (When you put food in the fridge, it lasts longer.)
4. Mama *stavlja* kolače da se peku u rerni. (Mom puts the cakes to bake in the oven.)
5. U restoranu mi *stavljaju* salvetu u krilo. (In the restaurant, they put a napkin on my lap.)
6. Učitelj *stavlja* ocene u dnevnik. (The teacher puts grades in the grade book.)
7. Oni *stavljaju* puno truda u svoj posao. (They put a lot of effort into their work.)
8. *Stavljam* tačku na ovu raspravu. (I'm putting an end to this discussion.)
9. On *stavlja* svoje potpise na ugovore. (He puts his signature on contracts.)
10. Kada *stavljate* kocke leda u piće, pripazite da ne poprskate. (When you put ice cubes in your drink, be careful not to spill.)